casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Bryant Martin COLLIER, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157839
COA: 336025 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 2, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 29, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
